trans-unit.source: Enables Windows authentication with client application services.
trans-unit.target: Aktiverar Windows-autentisering med klienten programtjänster.

trans-unit.source: You can use client application services to validate users by using Windows authentication.
trans-unit.target: Du kan använda programmet klienttjänster Validera användare med hjälp av Windows-autentisering.

trans-unit.source: To enable Windows authentication, you configure your application to use the ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider class.
trans-unit.target: Om du vill aktivera Windows-autentisering kan du konfigurera ditt program att använda klassen ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [How to: Configure Client Application Services](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Mer information finns i [så här: konfigurera klienten programtjänster](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: After configuration, you can validate users by calling the `static` <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.ValidateUser%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method.
trans-unit.target: Efter konfigurationen kan du validera användare genom att anropa den `static` <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.ValidateUser%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metod.</xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.ValidateUser%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.ValidateUser%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method internally calls the <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider.ValidateUser%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.ValidateUser%2A?displayProperty=fullName>internt metodanrop den <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider.ValidateUser%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider.ValidateUser%2A> </xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.ValidateUser%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider.ValidateUser%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method automatically authenticates the current user and sets the `static` <xref:System.Threading.Thread.CurrentPrincipal%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property to a <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.ClientRolePrincipal> object that contains the current <xref:System.Security.Principal.WindowsIdentity>.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider.ValidateUser%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoden autentiserar automatiskt den aktuella användaren och anger den `static` <xref:System.Threading.Thread.CurrentPrincipal%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen till ett <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.ClientRolePrincipal>objekt som innehåller aktuellt <xref:System.Security.Principal.WindowsIdentity>.</xref:System.Security.Principal.WindowsIdentity> </xref:System.Web.ClientServices.ClientRolePrincipal> </xref:System.Threading.Thread.CurrentPrincipal%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider.ValidateUser%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: If a <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientRoleProvider> is configured for your application, you can use the <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.ClientRolePrincipal> object to retrieve user role information from the roles service.
trans-unit.target: Om en <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientRoleProvider>har konfigurerats för programmet, du kan använda den <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.ClientRolePrincipal>datorobjektet för att hämta information om användaren rollen från tjänsten roller.</xref:System.Web.ClientServices.ClientRolePrincipal> </xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientRoleProvider>

trans-unit.source: You can retrieve a reference to the current ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider instance through the `static` <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.Provider%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: Du kan hämta en referens till den aktuella instansen ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider via den `static` <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.Provider%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskap.</xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.Provider%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: You can use the membership provider reference to call the <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider.ValidateUser%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method directly.
trans-unit.target: Du kan använda providern medlemskap för att anropa den <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider.ValidateUser%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoden direkt.</xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider.ValidateUser%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Additionally, you will need the membership provider reference to call the <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider.Logout%2A> method, which is not available in the <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipProvider> base class.
trans-unit.target: Dessutom behöver du medlemskap-providern för att anropa <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider.Logout%2A>metoden, som är inte tillgängligt i <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipProvider>grundläggande klass.</xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipProvider> </xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider.Logout%2A>

trans-unit.source: Logs out the user.
trans-unit.target: Loggar ut användaren.

trans-unit.source: For users authenticated through client application services, the `static` <xref:System.Threading.Thread.CurrentPrincipal%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property is set to a <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.ClientRolePrincipal> object that enables access to the configured role service.
trans-unit.target: För användare som autentiseras via klienten programtjänster, den `static` <xref:System.Threading.Thread.CurrentPrincipal%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskap är inställd på en <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.ClientRolePrincipal>objekt som ger åtkomst till den konfigurerade rolltjänsten.</xref:System.Web.ClientServices.ClientRolePrincipal> </xref:System.Threading.Thread.CurrentPrincipal%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The Logout method resets the <xref:System.Threading.Thread.CurrentPrincipal%2A> property to a <xref:System.Security.Principal.WindowsPrincipal> object that contains the current <xref:System.Security.Principal.WindowsIdentity>.
trans-unit.target: Logga ut metoden återställs <xref:System.Threading.Thread.CurrentPrincipal%2A>egenskapen till ett <xref:System.Security.Principal.WindowsPrincipal>objekt som innehåller aktuellt <xref:System.Security.Principal.WindowsIdentity>.</xref:System.Security.Principal.WindowsIdentity> </xref:System.Security.Principal.WindowsPrincipal> </xref:System.Threading.Thread.CurrentPrincipal%2A>

trans-unit.source: After you call this method, you can no longer retrieve roles for the user through the <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientRoleProvider> class.
trans-unit.target: När du anropar den här metoden kan du inte längre hämta roller för användaren med <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientRoleProvider>klass.</xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientRoleProvider>

trans-unit.source: To reauthenticate the current user, call the <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider.ValidateUser%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method.
trans-unit.target: Om du vill autentiseras den aktuella användaren anropar den <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider.ValidateUser%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoden.</xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider.ValidateUser%2A?displayProperty=fullName>
